That I am fully aware that my employer, the hereinafter referred to as EMPLOYER, intends to procure a Group Life Insurance package from both Sun Life Financial and Philam Life Insurance companies for participating employees of EMPLOYER, with the consent of employees and without any expense on their part;
That by signing this document, I have fully agreed and consented to the terms and conditions of EMPLOYER as to the disposition of the proceeds of the above-mentioned insurance policies if anything happens to undersigned during the effectivity of both insurance policies;
That I accept and agree to the sharing scheme of the insurance proceeds of said insurance policies, to wit:

I fully understand, accept and agree that the ten percent (10%) deduction is a necessary expense for the processing, follow-ups and miscellaneous expenses to claim the insurance proceeds of the life insurance, and that the fifty percent (50%) share of EMPLOYER in the insurance proceeds is both a necessary expense in processing the insurance claims and an indemnification to EMPLOYER for the ensuing operational difficulties, opportunity losses, expenses and losses in finding a replacement due to the untimely death of an employee;
I further fully understand and accept the full prerogative of EMPLOYER to pool the amounts generated from insurance proceeds mentioned above either in a trust fund or a special account to be used as payments for future insurance premiums of the abovementioned insurance policies or any insurance policies for their employees and for other employee benefits as may be adopted by EMPLOYER in the future;
NOW THEREFORE, premises considered, I hereby waive, in favor of EMPLOYER , ten percent (10%) of the insurance proceeds reimbursable by The Manufacturer's Life Insurance Company, Inc. and Philam Life Insurance companies in case I am hospitalized due to an accident, and I further waive fifty percent (50%) of the life insurance proceeds from both insurance companies mentioned above in case the undersigned dies either through natural cause or through accident.
Furthermore, I hereby constitiute the President of the Company, or any duly authorized representative of EMPLOYER, as my Attorney-in-Fact with full authority to transact with Sun Life Financial and Philam Life in the processing of all claims and to automatically deduct the amounts representing the above-mentioned percentages due to EMPLOYER from the insurance proceeds granted by both insurance companies.
I HAVE SATISFIED MYSELF FULLY AS TO THE NATURE OF THE OBLIGATIONS CONTAINED HEREIN AND HAVE SIGNED THIS WAIVER AND GRANT OF SPECIAL POWER OF ATTORNEY VOLUNTARILY.
